Act 351 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas As Engrossed: S3/6/25
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 SENATE BILL 317
4
5 By: Senator B. Johnson
6 By: Representatives Puryear, Achor, Andrews, Barker, Beaty Jr., Beck, Bentley, S. Berry, Breaux, Brooks,
7 K. Brown, M. Brown, N. Burkes, R. Burkes, Joey Carr, John Carr, Cavenaugh, Childress, C. Cooper,
8 Cozart, Crawford, Eaton, Evans, Furman, Gazaway, Gramlich, Hall, Hawk, Hollowell, L. Johnson, Long,
9 Lundstrum, Lynch, Maddox, McAlindon, McClure, M. McElroy, McGrew, B. McKenzie, McNair,
