11 Rose, Rye, Schulz, M. Shepherd, Torres, Tosh, Underwood, Unger, Vaught, Walker, Wing, Wooten
12
For An Act To Be Entitled
13
14 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW REGARDING HIGHER EDUCATION;
15 TO PROHIBIT AN INSTITUTION OF HIGHER EDUCATION FROM
16 PARTICIPATING IN CERTAIN ACTIVITIES WITH A PROHIBITED
17 FOREIGN PARTY; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
18
19
Subtitle
20
21 TO PROHIBIT AN INSTITUTION OF HIGHER
22 EDUCATION FROM PARTICIPATING IN CERTAIN
23 ACTIVITIES WITH A PROHIBITED FOREIGN
24 PARTY.
25
26 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
27
28 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 6, Chapter 60, Subchapter 1, is amended
29 to add an additional section to read as follows:
30 6-60-123. Prohibition on activities with prohibited foreign party —
31 Definition.
32 (a) As used in this section, "prohibited foreign party" means the same
33 as defined in § 18-11-802.
34 (b) An institution of higher education shall not participate in the
35 following activities with a prohibited foreign party:
36 (1) Conduct classified research;
*CRH050*
03-06-2025 14:17:03 CRH050
As Engrossed: S3/6/25 SB317
1 (2) Conduct agricultural research under a contract;
2 (3) Sell agricultural products, including without limitation
3 seeds;
4 (4) Engage in the production of agricultural products; or
5 (5) Enter into a nondisclosure agreement.
6
